							<p>As I mentioned last week, <a target="_blank" href="http://www.newwest.net/books" title="NewWest.Net/Books">NewWest.Net/Books</a> is sponsoring a Boulder get-together for writers, journalists, publishers, publicists, editors, writing teachers, book lovers, and all-around literary types.&nbsp; It&#8217;s an opportunity for people to make contacts in the local literary community.&nbsp; The event takes place at <a target="_blank" href="http://www.trilogywinebar.com/" title="Trilogy Wine Bar">Trilogy Wine Bar</a> on Monday, February 25, from 6 to 9 p.m.&nbsp; The guest list is filling up fast, so if you&#8217;d like to come, please send <script type="text/javascript">
